{"tid":1388873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"9am 東區法院 救義士啊！ ！ ！","createTime":"2019-07-30T19:06:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T01:03:39.000Z","uid":201575,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"adae2e28c3b0c0ec686e3fce37afbd35e1ae2d09","tid":1388873,"uid":201575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:06:11.000Z","msg":"義士無罪 釋放義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9387020fef93366de82c2c40eead682aabc3b7","tid":1388873,"uid":201575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:06:22.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"80cd69f8d1bfdd53a14cd39950e946874d313f95","tid":1388873,"uid":257299,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:13:06.000Z","msg":"阻阻你<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">廣傳，睇下會唔會有聽日既陪審團睇到。<br />\n<br />\n我地香港人依家得返最後呢條路。46個人已經被控暴動罪。求下瘋狂係撚咁推呢個post比全香港人知</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「陪審團否決權」是一個極少會被公開談論的題材，原因是一般大眾(尤其是陪審團成員)也不會被告知的一個權利，故被視為一項禁忌。</span></span>使用陪審團的刑事審訊中，陪審團的權力其實比法官還大，負責決定被告是否「有罪」，而其決定是不需要給予任何理由。若果陪審團決定被告罪名不成立，則被告會被當庭釋放。在普通法下，陪審團不需要為其裁決而負擔任何法律後果，而法官是必須跟隨陪審團的裁決而行事。另一方面，被告人是不能因為同一項刑事罪行而遭多次審訊，故在審訊後被判無罪是為最終判決，檢控機關是不能就同一罪名不服陪審團決定，提出上訴再提訊被告。<br />\n<br />\n因此，理論上若果陪審團認為有關的法律是「惡法」及/或認為司法系統腐敗僵化，成為政權利用惡法侵害公民的機器。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">則即使按照法律條文、法律原則、呈堂證據等皆應判被告「有罪」，**陪審團是有權力擇無視而判決被告「無罪」，即「犯法但無罪」。**</span></span><br />\n<br />\n在歷史上，普通法下存在的「陪審團否決權」往往是作為公民的陪審團成員，按照良心拯救同胞，對抗腐敗司法系統及政治的武器，從而達至正義。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uHzDtFF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuHzDtFF.png&h=b455b4d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10fc0854b8791cc3a481c80d4bb4784a0057cc40","tid":1388873,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T23:27:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6349656aded0f5d8f060d621bf932eefd1c4a336","tid":1388873,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T23:28:57.000Z","msg":"義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d896fd13ba5d23df1ff6cf23a98cc0a7cae51f","tid":1388873,"uid":263916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T23:31:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9aa7c66b91d0aeb350490a278dcc2e4463ba5818","tid":1388873,"uid":201575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T23:32:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a2f7c895881fcdb265193cbd8bda9c8fc31666","tid":1388873,"uid":14520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T23:43:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"800e1811d401647b841fbda400041b5fa7ea28eb","tid":1388873,"uid":209704,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:33:49.000Z","msg":"陪審團行使否決權無需理由<br />\n陪審團行使否決權無需理由"},{"pid":"a71e75cc2bcd9ba45c0d1cbbfed46f3ccac9882e","tid":1388873,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:37:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8abf3558d9d15cd63c9aa0089be218441e2134ac","tid":1388873,"uid":209704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:37:36.000Z","msg":"陪審團行使否決權無需理由<br />\n陪審團行使否決權無需理由<br />\n陪審團行使否決權無需理由"},{"pid":"7cdd8c43698a3c718173906dda0b90704b3c28d6","tid":1388873,"uid":209704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:38:32.000Z","msg":"陪審團行使否決權無需理由<br />\n陪審團行使否決權無需理由<br />\n陪審團行使否決權無需理由"},{"pid":"ed22d40ff3a78c41ae4c5f91e64c1f06f2a3e495","tid":1388873,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:40:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mNoQmxp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmNoQmxp.png&h=74ab50af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da4efd402800e452994c4a179d48fc0b80357583","tid":1388873,"uid":209704,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:41:24.000Z","msg":"今日會發生既事:<br />\n提堂黎講, 法庭書記會宣讀控罪, 法庭聽取答辯(Take Plea), 被告要回答認罪/唔認罪. 如果認罪，法庭聽取求情陳詞後就會考慮判刑, 如果唔認罪法官會將案件審訊排期移交至區域法院，之後批埋保釋同保釋條件, 被告去會計部交保釋金 (如果批保釋), 走得. (唔批就即時還押, unlikely)<br />\n<br />\n就算第一庭都好細, 一定入唔晒 (平時都爆), 會去支持既人入到既請記得熄電話, 保持安靜, 唔好叫口號, 庭出面都唔好亂黎, 一陣拉埋告你藐視法庭就hihi, 出法院就如常啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外, 區域法院唔會有陪審團, 所以好可惜另外一個Post講陪審團否決權 (<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1386844/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1386844/page/1</a>) 係不成立, 而點解去區域法院, 點解冇陪審團, 請追一追另一位巴打呢個Post (<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1387520/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1387520/page/1</a>), 亦請大家睇下入面既判詞, 你會為發現法庭同普通人對法律/正義既見解係好大出入<br />\n<br />\n睇完你可能覺得法例on9, 暴動咁易入?? 咁既法治狗也不屌<br />\n其實香港法官/司法系統已經算公道<br />\n唔公義係在於執法同立法 , 亦正正係訴求既重點<br />\n<br />\n希望義士能免除刑責 多謝你地既付出<br />\n大家加油 香港加油"},{"pid":"9191f56a950da3903260a2256a0c38de4fa5e5c1","tid":1388873,"uid":215419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:42:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e80a2e49d74ada0d3e0d556abce5716808da32b","tid":1388873,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:42:30.000Z","msg":"狗仲多過人 救命"},{"pid":"f245a1baf01ab548590ea373ddc614cdd35dc4c1","tid":1388873,"uid":209704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:42:35.000Z","msg":"推爆自由閪"},{"pid":"824e4ecf55cde7a06d84eb5776e2e03f92eb89d9","tid":1388873,"uid":250951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:45:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dea7c5ae2317ad5171bd14cd8f571036d9dd9aea","tid":1388873,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:48:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bfee33bdc6d708d84c238ee19f38ddaf6487b8ae","tid":1388873,"uid":80303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adae2e28c3b0c0ec686e3fce37afbd35e1ae2d09","tid":1388873,"uid":201575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:06:11.000Z","msg":"義士無罪 釋放義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:58:00.000Z","msg":"點救<br />\n劫獄咩"},{"pid":"3cd49fa0009b323e52f73a4168c2f7f9d1be230a","tid":1388873,"uid":149008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:03:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}